        <h2  >素馨呐的影评 &nbsp; &middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
        <span class="pl">( <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/cosmopolite7/reviews?cat_id=1002">19篇</a> )</span></h2>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
            <div class="pic">
                <a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/1299932/" title="Le salaire de la peur"><img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s2147368.jpg" alt="Le salaire de la peur"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>
                    <a title="经得起推敲与逼视的旅行" href="http://movie.douban.com/review/5536184/" class="title">经得起推敲与逼视的旅行</a>
                </h3>
                <div class="author">
